---
// Footer.astro
---
<footer class="bg-white border-t border-petalo-moss/10 pt-20 pb-10 px-6 md:px-12">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16">
    <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-petalo-moss rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-white text-[10px]">P</span>
        </div>
        <span class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-petalo-dark">Pétalo</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-petalo-dark/60 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Elevando el arte floral a una experiencia de lujo y sofisticación para tus momentos más memorables.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Navegación</h4>
      <ul class="text-sm text-petalo-dark/60 space-y-4">
        <li><a href="#inicio" class="hover:text-petalo-moss transition-colors">Inicio</a></li>
        <li><a href="#catalogo" class="hover:text-petalo-moss transition-colors">Catálogo</a></li>
        <li><a href="#servicios" class="hover:text-petalo-moss transition-colors">Servicios</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Contacto</h4>
      <ul class="text-sm text-petalo-dark/60 space-y-4">
        <li>contacto@petalo.com</li>
        <li>+52 (55) 1234-5678</li>
        <li>CDMX, México</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Newsletter</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-petalo-dark/60 mb-4">Suscríbete para recibir guías de cuidado y ofertas.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <input type="email" placeholder="Email" class="bg-petalo-cream border border-petalo-moss/10 rounded-petalo px-4 py-2 text-sm w-full outline-none focus:border-petalo-rose" />
        <button class="bg-petalo-moss text-white p-2 rounded-petalo">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"/><polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"/></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto pt-8 border-t border-petalo-moss/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-[10px] text-petalo-dark/40 uppercase tracking-widest">
    <p>© 2026 Pétalo Florería Boutique. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
    <div class="flex gap-6">
      <a href="#" class="hover:text-petalo-moss transition-colors">Instagram</a>
      <a href="#" class="hover:text-petalo-moss transition-colors">Pinterest</a>
      <a href="#" class="hover:text-petalo-moss transition-colors">Facebook</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>